data.description: Presenting this lovely 1690sf home with rare three car garage located in guard-gated 55+ Arizona Traditions community.  Step inside an open greatrm with neutral tile which flows through all footpaths. The spacious living & dining rooms open to a lovely kitchen boasting upgraded maple cabinets with tall 42'' uppers, even drawers for pots and pans! Black appliances & upgr laminate counters complement the beautiful cabinets! The primary bedrm is split with a ensuite bath, tub/shower combination, lg walk-in closet & private toilet. The Guest bedrm & bath at the front provides privacy for both! Plus a good-sized den or office! Ceiling fans grace most spaces. Step out to an extended covered patio with beautiful pavers & great outdoor kitchen! Mature plants, citrus trees and a fully-fenced yard!
